  @{b}@{u}@{fg highlight}BEKUNA version 2.1 (05.01.2006)@{ub}@{uu}@{fg text}

This is a automatically translation German->English

Please for the installation use "Installation".

"Bekuna Autostart" should always remain in the WBStartup drawer, even if Bekuna is not to be started automatically.
The start program "Bekuna start" can arbitrarily often be copied and thus can Bekuna be started at any time manually.

If your national language is not German or English, then adjust in the Locale Prefs as the 2nd language english, so that BEKUNA appears in english.

For further information please Bekuna.guide read!

@{b}***** Which I need? ***** @{ub}

- an Amiga with OS3.9
- RexxMast must run, of the Startup Sequence out.
- for instance 250KB free space on the partition SYSTEM: (SYS:)
- for instance 2MB free RAM.
- mind. 68020 CPU

A sceen size, small 640x480 is not to recommending.
For the moon diagram are mind. 256 colors necessarily.

Recommended for optimal representation:
- at least 68040
- graficboard
- at least 8MB RAM

@{b}***** which is again in version 2.1? ***** @{ub}

- calculating and show sunrise and sunset
- new adjustments
- the BekunaPrefs is in "Prefs" and can starts allon
